{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place walnuts and sesame seeds into mixing bowl and without measuring cup toast <nobr>10 min\/250°F\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Set mixing bowl aside and allow to cool15 minutes.","Once cooled, insert measuring cup into mixing bowl lid and grind <nobr>12 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and blend <nobr>8 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and blend a further <nobr>8 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>.","Add cooked beets, cream cheese, garlic, bread, cumin, lemon juice, salt and pepper and mix <nobr>15 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and mix a further <nobr>15 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>.","Check and adjust seasoning and transfer to a serving bowl, drizzle with olive oil and serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["2 ½ oz walnut halves or pieces","½ oz sesame seeds","10 ½ oz cooked beets, peeled, cut into pieces (approx. 1¼ in.)","3 oz cream cheese","1 garlic clove","1 oz stale bread, roughly torn (approx. 1 slice)","&frac18; tsp ground cumin","½ oz lemon juice","¼ tsp fine sea salt, to taste","2 pinches ground black pepper, to taste","¼ tsp salt, to taste","1 tbsp olive oil, to drizzle"]}],"id":"r106929","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-wkJZ_7GKhsg\/XZafqRBuS3I\/AAAAAAAAgwo\/XCOal5vSoksjnTDGsDc6IYZb1W8K4W2XQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_sqrU4Y76Usp16kuE.png","title":"Beet Hummus","publishedAt":"2017-03-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"4 g","fat":"16 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"10 g","calories":"782 kJ \/ 187 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving bowl","hintsAndTricks":["Roast your own beets or use vacuum packed pre-cooked beets, but not pickled beets. Raw beets can also be used for a different flavor.","How to roast your own beets: peel and cut into ¾ in. cubes and lightly rub with 1 tsp olive oil. Place beets in a baking pan and bake 25-30 minutes (400°F). Remove from oven and allow to cool.","Steam your beets: peel and cut beets into ¾ in. cubes and place into simmering basket. Add 20 oz water into mixing bowl and insert simmering basket with beets. Steam <nobr><strong>30 min\/Varoma\/speed 3<\/strong><\/nobr>.","Serve with pita bread or assorted sliced or whole raw vegetables."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","20m","1"]}